Package org.rcsb.mbt.model.attributes Description

Describes attributes that can be associated with 'StructureComponent' objects.

Attributes are secondary features of a structure component, describing characteristics such as color, radius, visibility, etc. Included here are several lookup classes, to look up colors by residue compound, for instance. Collective bundles of attributes, called 'styles' are also described here.
